# GitHub Linguist overrides
# See: https://github.com/github-linguist/linguist/blob/main/docs/overrides.md

# Treat Jekyll build plumbing as vendored so it does not dominate the language stats
Gemfile         linguist-vendored
Gemfile.lock    linguist-vendored
_config.yml     linguist-vendored

# This project is documentation. Count Markdown as the primary language.
*.md            linguist-detectable=true
*.md            linguist-documentation=false
